				<td colspan="2"><span>Pickup raids.... yeah ok been in a few. Pickup raids for PoP flag, namely the PoV dragon AD? NOoooo WAaaaay
<br />

<br />
This has got to be the most pathetic pickup raid in the history of pickup raiding i have ever been in. I am sure that there are probably some sucessful AD pickup raids, but the one i been in is just plain BAD.
<br />

<br />
How bad you ask? <b>60 dead people bad on the first AE bad</b>.
<br />

<br />
Most of these people coming to kill AD doesn't even know he can AE 3k, the raid leader even let some lvl 50s join. Does he ENJOY seeing them die?
<br />

<br />
No one even said a single word about DPS, I seriously wonder if they were actually PLANNING to.... what were they planning seriously I have no idea.
<br />

<br />
So ok the raid leader didn't give any info, fine, we as raider have the responsibility to know how to kill the mob ourselves, and I can tell you that exactly <b>60 dead peope</b> didn't know anything about it.
<br />

<br />
MBG heal? i wonder if ANY cleric in the raid even have this AA
<br />
DPS? <b>THEY ARE ALL DEAD</b>
<br />
RESIST? I was singing AE resist song, come on don't die like that, its embarassing.
<br />
KITE ADD? Did i mention they are all dead in the first AE?
<br />

<br />
The tank went down like pancake in a girls dorm, i mean come ON we didn't even have a 2nd MT ... we didn't have a MT list period... and why would we need one since we have <b>60 dead people</b>
<br />

<br />
my guild hates reflagging, want flag... go pickup? NOooo WAaaay
<br />

<br />
